<topic id="author-attributes-view">
  <title>Attributes View in Author Mode</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Author Editor<indexterm>attributes view</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p conkeyref="reusables-editing-modes/attribute-view-intro"/>
    <p>The view allows you to insert attributes or change the value of the already used attributes
      for the current editable element. An element is editable if any one of the following is
        true:<ul id="ul_nfn_z5r_n2">
        <li>The CSS stylesheet associated with the document does not specify a
            <uicontrol>false</uicontrol> value for the <xref
            href="../topics/dg-editable-css-extension.dita#dg-editable-css-extension" format="dita"
            >-oxy-editable</xref> property associated with the element.</li>
        <li>The element is entirely included in a deleted <xref
            href="../topics/author-change-tracking.dita#author-change-tracking/change-tracking"
            format="dita">Track Changes</xref> marker.</li>
        <li>The element is part of a content fragment that is referenced in
            <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> mode from another document.</li>
      </ul></p>
    <p conkeyref="reusables-editing-modes/attribute-view-rendering"/>
    <p conkeyref="reusables-editing-modes/attribute-view-sorting"/>
    <fig product="editor author">
      <title>The Attributes View</title>
      <image href="../img/sa_author_attributes_panel.png"/>
    </fig>
    <fig product="editorEclipse authorEclipse">
      <title>The Attributes View</title>
      <image href="../img/ec_author_attributes_panel.png"/>
    </fig>
    <p>A combo box located in the upper part of the view allows you to edit the attributes of the
      ancestors of the current element.</p>
    <p>The following actions are available in the contextual menu of the
        <uicontrol>Attributes</uicontrol> view when editing in <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> mode:<dl>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-modes/set-empty-value-dlentry">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-modes/remove-dlentry">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-modes/copy_dlentry">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-modes/paste_dlentry">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
      </dl></p>
    <section conkeyref="reusables-editing-modes/in-place-editor" id="in-place-attr-editor"/>
